  <!-- EN: heatshock -->
  <VRE_HeatshockHediff.label>热休克</VRE_HeatshockHediff.label>
  <!-- EN: A generalized disruption to body functioning caused by excessive exposure to heat and sun. The victim can produce heat shock proteins in response to high temperatures, which will prevent them from dying but will make them require more nutrition. Recovery is quick once in a cool area. -->
  <VRE_HeatshockHediff.description>长时间暴露于高温和日晒的环境下导致的患者体内温度平衡失调状态。此时的患者会合成一种特殊的热休克蛋白，使其可以在最为酷热的环境中生存和活动，但所需进食量也相应增加了。热休克会在患者进入凉快的地方后随着时间的推移自然恢复。</VRE_HeatshockHediff.description>
