  <!-- EN: heatstress -->
  <VRE_HeatstressHediff.label>热应激</VRE_HeatstressHediff.label>
  <!-- EN: A generalized disruption to body functioning caused by excessive exposure to heat and sun. Celular damage and denaturation of proteins will cause burn damage and will very quickly cause loss of consciousness. -->
  <VRE_HeatstressHediff.description>长时间暴露于高温和日晒的环境下导致的患者体内温度平衡失调状态。这不仅会引起蛋白质变性、烧伤、疼痛以及严重恐火，还会降低意识和移动能力。</VRE_HeatstressHediff.description>
