  <!-- EN: hypothermic hibernation -->
  <VRE_HypothermicHibernationHediff.label>低温冬眠</VRE_HypothermicHibernationHediff.label>
  <!-- EN: This person will enter a hibernation if their temperatures drop below a certain point for too long. They will rapidly lose their body functions and fall into a deep sleep, which prevents any sort of frostbite damages but also makes them unable to do anything. -->
  <VRE_HypothermicHibernationHediff.description>此人因暴露于低温中而陷入了“低温冬眠”状态，其身体机能会逐渐丧失，直到完全沉睡。虽然能使此人不被冻伤，但也会失去行动能力。</VRE_HypothermicHibernationHediff.description>
